#: ../../R/reality-check.rst:5
msgid "reality check"
msgstr "reality check"

#: ../../R/reality-check.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../R/reality-check.rst:10
msgid ""
"The simplest kind of test of software or hardware; doing the equivalent of "
"asking it what ``2 + 2`` is and seeing if you get 4. The software equivalent"
" of a :ref:`smoke-test`\\."
msgstr ""
"ソフトウェアやハードウェアの最も単純な種類のテスト。\\ ``2 + 2``\\ は何かと尋ねて4が得られるか見るのに相当することを行うこと。\\ "
":ref:`smoke-test`\\ のソフトウェア版。"

#: ../../R/reality-check.rst:14
msgid ""
"The act of letting a :ref:`real-user` try out prototype software. Compare "
":ref:`sanity-check`\\."
msgstr "\\ :ref:`real-user`\\ にプロトタイプソフトウェアを試させる行為。\\ :ref:`sanity-check`\\ と比較せよ。"
